<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fff7f0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #4b2e2e;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #fffdfc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #f3d1c4;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #fbbf24;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #4b2e2e;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #10b981;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #fff7f0;
      color: #6b4c40;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content, .header, .footer {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .button {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reset Your Password üîê</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{data.firstname}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset your Kindora account password. Click the button below to create a new one. This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>

      <a href="{{data.clientUrl}}/auth/reset-password?token={{data.token}}" target="_blank" class="button">Reset Password</a>

      <p>If you didn‚Äôt ask for this, no worries ‚Äî you can simply ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      With care and safety,<br />
      ‚Äî The Kindora Team üíõ
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
